snippet.title: Super Skramble! on a Commodore 64
snippet.description:
Super Skramble! © 1983 Terminal Software

Programmed by R.W. Stevens

Hardware used: C64C and 1541-II floppy disk drive.
Captured with Terratec Grabby.

Note: The loading time has been cut from the video to save time for gameplay. It does not load this fast from the floppy disks!
